\begin{equation}
\nabla^T_a\nabla^{T\,a}\phi .
\end{equation}

The potential contribution produces:

\begin{equation}
\frac{\partial V_T}{\partial \phi}.
\end{equation}

Additional curvature and torsion couplings are collected as:

\begin{equation}
\mathcal{C}_{RT}
+
\mathcal{C}_{\tau}.
