Therefore the field equation takes the form:

\begin{equation}
\boxed{
\nabla^T_a\nabla^{T\,a}\phi
+
\frac{\partial V_T}{\partial \phi}
+
\mathcal{C}_{RT}
+
\mathcal{C}_{\tau}
